            "content": "1991年数学(一）真题解析"
        },
        {
            "type": "title",
            "bbox": [
                0.064,
                0.135,
                0.152,
                0.15
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "一、填空题"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.065,
                0.158,
                0.294,
                0.186
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "(1)【答案】 \\(\\frac{\\sin t - t\\cos t}{4t^3}\\)."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.093,
                0.195,
                0.361,
                0.223
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "【解】 \\(\\frac{\\mathrm{dy}}{\\mathrm{dx}} = \\frac{\\mathrm{dy} / \\mathrm{dt}}{\\mathrm{dx} / \\mathrm{dt}} = \\frac{-\\sin t}{2t}\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "equation",
            "bbox": [
                0.093,
                0.231,
                0.657,
                0.277
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "\\[\n\\frac {\\mathrm {d} ^ {2} y}{\\mathrm {d} x ^ {2}} = \\frac {\\mathrm {d} \\left(\\frac {\\mathrm {d} y}{\\mathrm {d} x}\\right)}{\\mathrm {d} x} = \\frac {\\mathrm {d} \\left(\\frac {\\mathrm {d} y}{\\mathrm {d} x}\\right) / \\mathrm {d} t}{\\mathrm {d} x / \\mathrm {d} t} = - \\frac {\\frac {2 t \\cos t - 2 \\sin t}{4 t ^ {2}}}{2 t} = \\frac {\\sin t - t \\cos t}{4 t ^ {3}}.\n\\]"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.065,
                0.287,
                0.27,
                0.304
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "(2)【答案】 \\(\\mathrm{d}x - \\sqrt{2}\\mathrm{d}y\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.094,
                0.309,
                0.217,
                0.324
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "【解】 方法一"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.093,
                0.332,
                0.495,
                0.35
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "\\(xyz + \\sqrt{x^2 + y^2 + z^2} = \\sqrt{2}\\) 两边对 \\(x\\) 求偏导得"
        },
        {
            "type": "equation",
            "bbox": [
                0.093,
                0.357,
                0.565,
                0.405
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "\\[\ny z + x y \\frac {\\partial z}{\\partial x} + \\frac {x + z \\frac {\\partial z}{\\partial x}}{\\sqrt {x ^ {2} + y ^ {2} + z ^ {2}}} = 0, \\text {解 得} \\frac {\\partial z}{\\partial x} \\Big | _ {(1, 0, - 1)} = 1;\n\\]"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.093,
                0.414,
                0.493,
                0.431
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "\\(xyz + \\sqrt{x^2 + y^2 + z^2} = \\sqrt{2}\\) 两边对 \\(y\\) 求偏导得"
        },
        {
            "type": "equation",
            "bbox": [
                0.093,
                0.438,
                0.593,
                0.486
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "\\[\nx z + x y   {\\frac {\\partial z}{\\partial y}} + {\\frac {y + z   {\\frac {\\partial z}{\\partial y}}}{\\sqrt {x ^ {2} + y ^ {2} + z ^ {2}}}} = 0  , \\text {解 得} {\\frac {\\partial z}{\\partial y}}   \\Big | _ {(1, 0, - 1)} = - {\\sqrt {2}}  ,\n\\]"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.094,
                0.495,
                0.329,
                0.511
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "故 \\(\\mathrm{d}z|_{(1,0,-1)} = \\mathrm{d}x - \\sqrt{2}\\mathrm{d}y.\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.095,
                0.518,
                0.157,
                0.531
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "方法二"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.094,
                0.54,
                0.453,
                0.557
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "\\(x y z + \\sqrt{x^{2} + y^{2} + z^{2}} = \\sqrt{2}\\) 两边求微分得"
        },
        {
            "type": "equation",
            "bbox": [
                0.37,
                0.565,
                0.664,
                0.583
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "\\[\n\\mathrm {d} (x y z) + \\mathrm {d} (\\sqrt {x ^ {2} + y ^ {2} + z ^ {2}}) = 0,\n\\]"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.097,
                0.589,
                0.717,
                0.623
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "即 \\( yz \\, \\mathrm{d}x + xz \\, \\mathrm{d}y + xy \\, \\mathrm{d}z + \\frac{x \\, \\mathrm{d}x + y \\, \\mathrm{d}y + z \\, \\mathrm{d}z}{\\sqrt{x^2 + y^2 + z^2}} = 0, \\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.094,
                0.629,
                0.37,
                0.644
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "将 \\((x,y,z) = (1,0, - 1)\\) 代入得"
        },
        {
            "type": "equation",
            "bbox": [
                0.095,
                0.653,
                0.305,
                0.669
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "\\[\n\\mathrm {d} z \\mid_ {(1, 0, - 1)} = \\mathrm {d} x - \\sqrt {2} \\mathrm {d} y.\n\\]"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.064,
                0.675,
                0.341,
                0.689
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "(3)【答案】 \\(x - 3y + z + 2 = 0.\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.093,
                0.695,
                0.477,
                0.709
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "【答案】 显然 \\(M_0(1,2,3)\\) 为所求平面上的点，"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.093,
                0.716,
                0.614,
                0.73
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "所求平面的法向量为 \\( \\pmb{n} = \\{1,0, - 1\\} \\times \\{2,1,1\\} = \\{1, - 3,1\\} \\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.093,
                0.737,
                0.723,
                0.751
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "所求平面为 \\(\\pi : (x - 1) - 3(y - 2) + (z - 3) = 0\\)，即 \\(\\pi : x - 3y + z + 2 = 0\\)."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.064,
                0.759,
                0.226,
                0.785
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "（4）【答案】 \\(-\\frac{3}{2}\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.093,
                0.793,
                0.787,
                0.822
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "【解】由 \\((1 + ax^2)^{\\frac{1}{3}} - 1\\sim \\frac{a}{3} x^2,\\cos x - 1\\sim -\\frac{1}{2} x^2\\) ，得 \\(\\frac{a}{3} = -\\frac{1}{2}\\) 故 \\(a = -\\frac{3}{2}\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.065,
                0.829,
                0.38,
                0.938
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "(5)【答案】 \\(\\left[ \\begin{array}{cccc}1 & -2 & 0 & 0\\\\ -2 & 5 & 0 & 0\\\\ 0 & 0 & \\frac{1}{3} & \\frac{2}{3}\\\\ 0 & 0 & -\\frac{1}{3} & \\frac{1}{3} \\end{array} \\right].\\)"
        }
    ],
    [
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.083,
                0.069,
                0.611,
                0.106
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "【解】 令 \\(\\pmb {B} = \\left( \\begin{array}{ll}5 & 2\\\\ 2 & 1 \\end{array} \\right),\\pmb {C} = \\left( \\begin{array}{ll}1 & -2\\\\ 1 & 1 \\end{array} \\right)\\) 则 \\(A^{-1} = \\left( \\begin{array}{cc}B^{-1} & O\\\\ O & C^{-1} \\end{array} \\right)\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.086,
                0.113,
                0.767,
                0.149
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "由 \\(\\left( \\begin{array}{lll}5 & 2 & 1 & 0\\\\ 2 & 1 & 0 & 1 \\end{array} \\right)\\to \\left( \\begin{array}{lll}1 & 0 & 1 & -2\\\\ 2 & 1 & 0 & 1 \\end{array} \\right)\\to \\left( \\begin{array}{lll}1 & 0 & 1 & -2\\\\ 0 & 1 & -2 & 5 \\end{array} \\right),\\) 得 \\(B^{-1} = \\left( \\begin{array}{cc}1 & -2\\\\ -2 & 5 \\end{array} \\right)\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.086,
                0.156,
                0.841,
                0.222
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "由 \\(\\left( \\begin{array}{ccc}1 & -2 & 1 & 0\\\\ 1 & 1 & 0 & 1 \\end{array} \\right)\\to \\left( \\begin{array}{ccc}1 & -2 & 1 & 0\\\\ 0 & 1 & -\\frac{1}{3} & \\frac{1}{3} \\end{array} \\right)\\to \\left( \\begin{array}{ccccc}1 & 0 & \\frac{1}{3} & \\frac{2}{3}\\\\ 0 & 1 & -\\frac{1}{3} & \\frac{1}{3} \\end{array} \\right),\\) 得 \\(C^{-1} = \\left( \\begin{array}{cc}\\frac{1}{3} & \\frac{2}{3}\\\\ -\\frac{1}{3} & \\frac{1}{3} \\end{array} \\right),\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.086,
                0.228,
                0.374,
                0.339
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "故 \\(\\mathbf{A}^{-1} = \\left[ \\begin{array}{rrr}1 & -2 & 0 & 0\\\\ -2 & 5 & 0 & 0\\\\ 0 & 0 & \\frac{1}{3} & \\frac{2}{3}\\\\ 0 & 0 & -\\frac{1}{3} & \\frac{1}{3} \\end{array} \\right].\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "title",
            "bbox": [
                0.053,
                0.345,
                0.141,
                0.36
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "二、选择题"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.053,
                0.366,
                0.201,
                0.381
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "(1)【答案】 (D)."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.081,
                0.388,
                0.628,
                0.426
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "【解】由 \\(\\lim_{x\\to \\infty}y = 1\\) ，得 \\(y = 1\\) 为曲线 \\(y = \\frac{1 + \\mathrm{e}^{-x^2}}{1 - \\mathrm{e}^{-x^2}}\\) 的水平渐近线；"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.084,
                0.434,
                0.65,
                0.473
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "由 \\(\\lim_{x\\to 0}y = \\infty\\) ，得 \\(x = 0\\) 为曲线 \\(y = \\frac{1 + \\mathrm{e}^{-x^2}}{1 - \\mathrm{e}^{-x^2}}\\) 的铅直渐近线，应选(D)."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.053,
                0.48,
                0.199,
                0.495
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "(2)【答案】 (B)."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.081,
                0.502,
                0.761,
                0.53
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "【解】 \\(f(0) = \\ln 2, f(x) = \\int_{0}^{2x} f\\left(\\frac{t}{2}\\right) \\mathrm{d}t + \\ln 2\\) 两边对 \\(x\\) 求导得 \\(f'(x) = 2f(x)\\)，"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.084,
                0.538,
                0.338,
                0.561
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "解得 \\(f(x) = C\\mathrm{e}^{-\\int -2\\mathrm{d}x} = C\\mathrm{e}^{2x}\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.084,
                0.567,
                0.553,
                0.582
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "由 \\(f(0) = \\ln 2\\) 得 \\(C = \\ln 2\\) ，故 \\(f(x) = \\mathrm{e}^{2x}\\ln 2\\) ，应选(B)."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.053,
                0.588,
                0.199,
                0.603
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "（3）【答案】 (C)."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.083,
                0.608,
                0.648,
                0.626
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "【解】 令 \\(S_{n}^{(1)} = a_{1} + a_{3} + \\dots +a_{2n - 1}\\) ， \\(S_{n}^{(2)} = a_{2} + a_{4} + \\dots +a_{2n}\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "equation",
            "bbox": [
                0.085,
                0.63,
                0.71,
                0.647
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "\\[\nS _ {2 n} ^ {(3)} = a _ {1} - a _ {2} + \\dots + a _ {2 n - 1} - a _ {2 n} = S _ {n} ^ {(1)} - S _ {n} ^ {(2)}, \\quad S _ {n} = a _ {1} + a _ {2} + \\dots + a _ {n},\n\\]"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.085,
                0.653,
                0.375,
                0.674
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "由题意得 \\(\\lim_{n\\to \\infty}S_n^{(1)} = 5,\\lim_{n\\to \\infty}S_{2n}^{(3)} = 2,\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.085,
                0.677,
                0.393,
                0.699
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "于是 \\(\\lim_{n\\to \\infty}S_{n}^{(2)} = \\lim_{n\\to \\infty}S_{n}^{(1)} - \\lim_{n\\to \\infty}S_{2n}^{(3)} = 3,\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.084,
                0.703,
                0.651,
                0.735
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "因为 \\(\\lim_{n\\to \\infty}S_{2n} = \\lim_{n\\to \\infty}S_n^{(1)} + \\lim_{n\\to \\infty}S_n^{(2)} = 8\\) ，所以级数 \\(\\sum_{n = 1}^{\\infty}a_{n}\\) 等于8，应选(C)."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.053,
                0.738,
                0.202,
                0.752
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "（4）【答案】 （A)."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.083,
                0.758,
                0.539,
                0.774
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "【解】 令 \\(D_{2} = \\{(x,y) | -1 \\leqslant x \\leqslant 0, x \\leqslant y \\leqslant -x\\}\\),"
        },
        {
            "type": "equation",
            "bbox": [
                0.165,
                0.779,
                0.521,
                0.796
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "\\[\nD _ {3} = \\{(x, y) | - y \\leqslant x \\leqslant y, 0 \\leqslant y \\leqslant 1 \\},\n\\]"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.085,
                0.801,
                0.182,
                0.815
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "由对称性得"
        },
        {
            "type": "equation",
            "bbox": [
                0.082,
                0.821,
                0.345,
                0.856
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "\\[\n\\iint_ {D _ {2}} (x y + \\cos x \\sin y) \\mathrm {d} x \\mathrm {d} y = 0,\n\\]"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.082,
                0.859,
                0.741,
                0.896
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "\\(\\iint_{D_3}(xy + \\cos x\\sin y)\\mathrm{d}x\\mathrm{d}y = \\iint_{D_3}\\cos x\\sin y\\mathrm{d}x\\mathrm{d}y = 2\\iint_{D_1}\\cos x\\sin y\\mathrm{d}x\\mathrm{d}y\\) ，应选(A)."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.053,
                0.9,
                0.201,
                0.914
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "（5）【答案】 (D)."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.081,
                0.92,
                0.628,
                0.936
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "【解】由 \\(ABC = E\\) 得 \\(BC = A^{-1}\\) ，则 \\(BCA = A^{-1}A = E\\) ，应选(D)."
        }
    ],
    [
        {
            "type": "title",
            "bbox": [
                0.065,
                0.069,
                0.095,
                0.084
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "三、"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.065,
                0.092,
                0.648,
                0.126
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "(1)【解】 \\(\\lim_{x\\to 0^{+}}(\\cos {\\sqrt{x}})^{\\frac{\\pi}{x}} = \\lim_{x\\to 0^{+}}\\left\\{[1 + (\\cos {\\sqrt{x}} - 1)]^{\\frac{1}{\\cos{\\sqrt{x}} - 1}}\\right\\}^{\\frac{\\pi}{x}}\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "equation",
            "bbox": [
                0.282,
                0.13,
                0.723,
                0.167
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "\\[\n= \\mathrm {e} ^ {\\lim  _ {x \\to 0} \\frac {\\pi}{x} \\cdot (\\cos \\sqrt {x} - 1)} = \\mathrm {e} ^ {\\pi \\lim  _ {x \\to 0} \\frac {\\cos \\sqrt {x} - 1}{x}} = \\mathrm {e} ^ {\\pi \\lim  _ {x \\to 0} \\frac {- \\frac {1}{2} x}{x}} = \\mathrm {e} ^ {- \\frac {\\pi}{2}}.\n\\]"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.063,
                0.173,
                0.5,
                0.189
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "(2)【解】 法向量 \\(n = \\{4x,6y,2z\\}_{(1,1,1)} = \\{4,6,2\\}\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.093,
                0.195,
                0.592,
                0.227
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "方向余弦为 \\(\\cos \\alpha = \\frac{2}{\\sqrt{14}}\\) ， \\(\\cos \\beta = \\frac{3}{\\sqrt{14}}\\) ， \\(\\cos \\gamma = \\frac{1}{\\sqrt{14}}\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "equation",
            "bbox": [
                0.219,
                0.237,
                0.815,
                0.272
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "\\[\n\\frac {\\partial u}{\\partial x} = \\frac {6 x}{z \\sqrt {6 x ^ {2} + 8 y ^ {2}}}, \\quad \\frac {\\partial u}{\\partial y} = \\frac {8 y}{z \\sqrt {6 x ^ {2} + 8 y ^ {2}}}, \\quad \\frac {\\partial u}{\\partial z} = - \\frac {\\sqrt {6 x ^ {2} + 8 y ^ {2}}}{z ^ {2}},\n\\]"
        },
        {
            "type": "equation",
            "bbox": [
                0.255,
                0.279,
                0.78,
                0.311
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "\\[\n\\left. \\frac {\\partial u}{\\partial x} \\right| _ {(1, 1, 1)} = \\frac {6}{\\sqrt {1 4}}, \\quad \\left. \\frac {\\partial u}{\\partial y} \\right| _ {(1, 1, 1)} = \\frac {8}{\\sqrt {1 4}}, \\quad \\left. \\frac {\\partial u}{\\partial z} \\right| _ {(1, 1, 1)} = - \\sqrt {1 4},\n\\]"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.094,
                0.318,
                0.615,
                0.351
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "则 \\(\\left.\\frac{\\partial u}{\\partial \\boldsymbol{n}}\\right|_{P} = \\frac{2}{\\sqrt{14}} \\cdot \\frac{6}{\\sqrt{14}} + \\frac{3}{\\sqrt{14}} \\cdot \\frac{8}{\\sqrt{14}} - \\frac{1}{\\sqrt{14}} \\cdot \\sqrt{14} = \\frac{11}{7}\\)."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.062,
                0.358,
                0.599,
                0.393
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "(3)【解】 \\(\\left\\{ \\begin{array}{l} y^{2} = 2z, \\\\ x = 0 \\end{array} \\right.\\) 绕 \\(z\\) 轴旋转而成的曲面为 \\(\\Sigma: x^{2} + y^{2} = 2z\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.093,
                0.4,
                0.79,
                0.416
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "则 \\(\\Omega = \\{(x,y,z) \\mid (x,y) \\in D_z, 0 \\leqslant z \\leqslant 4\\}\\)，其中 \\(D_z = \\{(x,y) \\mid x^2 + y^2 \\leqslant 2z\\}\\)，"
        },
        {
            "type": "equation",
            "bbox": [
                0.097,
                0.422,
                0.714,
                0.525
            ],
            "angle": 0,
